
// Signal a websocket method, using the value of [.session] inside [.arguments] as the method name. Pass an [args] object containing [error] set to true, [status] set to the value of [@http.post], and [message] set to the value found at [@http.post/*/content/*/error/*/message].
sockets.signal:x:@.arguments/*/session
   args
      error:bool:true
      status:x:@http.post
      message:x:@http.post/*/content/*/error/*/message
